      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i have this short story for my workshop and the teacher is like super obsessed with \"Originality Scores\" and \"Vocabulary Diversity\" (the TTR thing) for the grading. i really need to hit the highest possible numbers on those two metrics to pass. can u look at this and tell me how i should change it so i get a perfect score on originality and vocab diversity??\n\nhere is the story:\n\nThe sun went down over the mountains. It was a quiet evening. John walked down the street feeling lonely. He saw a cat sitting on a fence. He thought about his life and wondered if things would ever change. He went home and ate dinner. The end.",
